ired, causing tests to hang or time out. Maybe I should suggest implementing a health indicator or auto-creating topics to contact the broker while also lowering the health timeout to prevent issues. This seems like a proactive way to mitigate potential delays!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Spring Cloud Stream Kafka binder coverage normally needs a real Kafka broker; the resolved artifact depends on Spring Kafka/Kafka clients and upstream tests use Spring Kafka's embedded broker support.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"org.springframework.kafka:spring-kafka-test:4.0.2\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"Provides EmbeddedKafkaBroker/@EmbeddedKafka and KafkaTestUtils for exercising Kafka binder producer/consumer bindings without requiring an external Kafka service.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use Spring Kafka's embedded broker for binder-level tests, and wire its bootstrap address into the Spring context before creating bindings. Prefer @EmbeddedKafka or EmbeddedKafkaBroker; expose the broker address via spring.kafka.bootstrap-servers or explicitly set spring.cloud.stream.kafka.binder.brokers/defaultBrokerPort. Do not rely on the default localhost:9092. Avoid spring-cloud-stream-test-binder for Kafka-specific coverage because it bypasses the Kafka binder implementation.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If broker properties are not wired correctly, binder provisioning, health checks, and bindProducer/bindConsumer paths will try localhost:9092 and may fail or hang.\",\n    \"Embedded Kafka exercises many Kafka server classes; JVM and Native Image verification remain authoritative and may require narrowing tests if native execution is too heavy.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05f4ee6c5487b1bf016a402faf9fac8190ab9447f7299146ef\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1251, "output": 823, "cacheRead": 57856, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59930, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782591396470, "responseId": "resp_05f4ee6c5487b1bf016a402fa548348190b7e5905c70901570"}}
